Package: wordcomments
Title: Extract and Analyze Comments from Word Documents
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alexandros", "Rammos", , "vd18986@bristol.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A toolkit for extracting, analyzing, and managing comments from 
    Microsoft Word (.docx) documents. Features include comment extraction with 
    full metadata, thread detection for comment conversations, filtering by 
    reviewer, summary statistics, and export to multiple formats. Particularly 
    useful for academic manuscript revision workflows and collaborative document 
    review.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
